# Copy to .dev.vars (not committed) — wrangler local dev secrets
# Used by CF Pages Functions when running `wrangler pages dev` or `npm run dev`.
#
# Production/Preview equivalents live in:
# Cloudflare Dashboard → Pages → trip-planner → Settings → Environment variables

# Mapbox Directions API token (public pk.* token, for /api/route proxy)
# Get one free at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.ey...your-token-here
